{"list":[{"title":"目的","data":"<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:28px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑\">知道氢氧化铝具有两性，既能与强酸反应，也能与强碱反应。</span></span></span></span></p>"},{"title":"原理","data":"<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\"><span style=\"font-size:28px\">Al(OH)<sub>3</sub>&nbsp;+ 3HCl = AlCl<sub>3 </sub>+ 3H<sub>2</sub>O</span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\"><span style=\"font-size:28px\">Al(OH)<sub>3</sub>&nbsp;+ NaOH = NaAlO<sub>2</sub>&nbsp;+ 2H<sub>2</sub>O</span></span></p>"},{"title":"用品","data":"<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:28px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman'\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑\">仪器：</span></span><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑\">试管架、试管、药匙、胶头滴管。</span></span></span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:28px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman'\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑\">药品：</span></span><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑\">氢氧化铝、稀盐酸、氢氧化钠溶液。</span></span></span></span></p>"},{"title":"步骤","data":"<p><span style=\"font-size:28px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑\">分别在两支试管中加入少量氢氧化铝，然后分别加入稀盐酸和氢氧化钠溶液，观察实验现象。</span></span></span></span></p>"},{"title":"现象","data":"<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:28px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑\">氢氧化铝溶解，形成无色溶液。</span></span></span></span></p>"}],"x":0,"y":0,"width":600,"height":600}